detailedDescription: Ground floor self-contained refurbished entrance and reception 1st and 2nd floor refurbished offices Lift Excellent natural light 10 on-site parking spaces Suspended ceilings with integral lighting Newly double glazed windows front and back Additional car park available close by at £700 PA per space

The Universal Building at 364 Kensington High St comprises 38,475 sq ft of newly refurbished offices. Featuring a large double height, manned reception, showers, secure bike storage and communal roof terrace. The building is Hyperoptic ready and also has a landlord's broadband service cabled to each floor with 100MB for £250 per month. Up to 1GB available. Located next door to the New Olympia Development, which will be ready in 2024. Rents from £39.50 per sq ft Flexible leases available
c.7,000 sq ft yard Can take 25-30 cars approx Secure, self contained yard Up to 12 month lease available.
